or is likely to occur.

2. A significant change in catch or bycatch composition for a specific fishery or fleet component has occurred, or
is likely to occur.

3. Unanticipated shortfalls in the North Pacific Fishery Observer Fund require decreased observer coverage to maintain
solvency of the observer programs.






