again, in writing, facsimile copy, or by telephone, no less than 10 days prior to the need for an observer, to make final
arrangements for observer deployment. Names of observer contractors, information for contacting contractors,
and a list of embarkment/disembarkment ports for observers will be published in the 

Federal Register

 annually prior to the beginning of the calendar year (see  677.11). 

