<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY: 

The Civilian Agency Acquisition Council and the Defense Acquisition Regulations Council are proposing changes
to the Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) to amend FAR policies and clauses on Prompt Payment. This proposed rule,
in combination with changes made by Federal Acquisition Circular 84-45, dated March 31, 1989, will complete
the implementation of changes made in OMB Circular A-125 (Revised), dated December 12, 1989, to comply with
